headline: Analog Devices price target raised to $280 from $254 at Evercore ISI
summary: Evercore ISI raised the firm’s price target on Analog Devices (ADI) to $280 from $254 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The firm believes guidance contemplates a cautious supply chain, which has undergone seven quarters of inventory correction and is heading to below “normal” levels.
